## Phase 1.5 — Inspection Trigger Completion  
**(COMPLETE)**

> **Purpose:** Ensure inspections occur *only* at correct player-action boundaries.

### Completed Wiring

| Trigger | Status |
|------|------|
| System entry clearance | ✔ Deterministic, arrival-only |
| Legal cargo sale | ✔ Pressure-gated + deterministic |
| Port departure clearance | ✔ Post-affordability, pre-mutation |

### Guardrails Enforced

- All triggers are player-action boundaries
- All triggers are deterministic and pressure-gated
- No trigger mutates cargo, credits, or documents
- No trigger blocks player action

### Outcome

- Inspections feel consistent and fair
- No “phantom” inspections on failed actions
- Logs align with player expectations

✅ **Phase 1.5 is complete and closed.**

